OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FGenerally fine and dry, with
OL,6,Flight winds and bright spells, though
OL,7,Foften rather cloudy. Some sunny spells
OL,8,Fmay develop through the afternoon,
OL,9,Fespecially in the east. Turning warmer.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FBright
OL,12,Fbut increasingly cloudy on Monday,
OL,13,Fsome possible rain late. Breezy and
OL,14,Fcloudier on Tuesday and Wednesday,
OL,15,Fwith outbreaks of rain at times,
OL,16,Fperhaps locally heavy. Temperatures
OL,17,Fnear normal.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
